      <div class="post-title">EU AI Act Compliance Checklist for AI Agents (2026 Deadline)</div>
      <div class="post-desc">Everything your AI agent needs to comply with the EU AI Act before August 1, 2026. Step-by-step technical checklist covering identity, audit trails, human oversight, and registration.</div>
      <div class="post-meta">May 7, 2026 · 8 min read</div>
      <div class="post-arrow">Read article →</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/blog/high-risk-ai-agent-eu-ai-act.html" class="post-card">
      <div class="post-tag">EU AI Act · High Risk</div>
      <div class="post-title">What Happens If Your AI Agent Is Classified as High-Risk Under the EU AI Act?</div>
      <div class="post-desc">High-risk AI agent classification triggers strict legal obligations. Learn which agents qualify as high-risk, what conformity assessment requires, and what fines look like.</div>
