      <div class="post-desc">A step-by-step guide to generating verifiable EU AI Act compliance evidence for your AI agent. Free tools, no signup required, takes exactly 5 minutes.</div>
      <div class="post-meta">May 7, 2026 · 4 min read</div>
      <div class="post-arrow">Read article →</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/blog/ssl-moment-ai-agents.html" class="post-card">
      <div class="post-tag">Technical Insight</div>
      <div class="post-title">AI Agent Identity: The SSL Moment for Autonomous Systems</div>
      <div class="post-desc">Why cryptographic agent identity is the defining infrastructure challenge of the agentic era — and how it mirrors the SSL moment that made the web trustworthy.</div>
      <div class="post-meta">May 7, 2026 · 7 min read</div>
      <div class="post-arrow">Read article →</div>
    </a>

    <a href="/blog/nist-ai-rmf-vs-eu-ai-act.html" class="post-card">
      <div class="post-tag">Compliance Frameworks</div>
      <div class="post-title">NIST AI Risk Management Framework vs EU AI Act: What Developers Need to Know</div>
      <div class="post-desc">A practical comparison of NIST AI RMF and EU AI Act requirements for AI agent developers. Key differences, overlaps, and how to satisfy both frameworks simultaneously.</div>
      <div class="post-meta">May 7, 2026 · 7 min read</div>
      <div class="post-arrow">Read article →</div>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<footer>
